1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,720
[EP. 03] Before the Night is Gone

2
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:20,700
Lee Yeo Reum…

3
00:00:20,700 --> 00:00:23,460
Why did she drink so much?

4
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:26,900
She should be more cautious…

5
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:30,240
But…

6
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:34,980
Why are you… always looking the other way?

7
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:37,460
I know you like that other guy but

8
00:00:37,460 --> 00:00:39,160
I just can’t give up on you…

9
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:42,210
Actually I don’t know

10
00:00:42,210 --> 00:00:44,200
what I want to do with you.

11
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:47,100
Is it enough for me to be your friend

12
00:00:47,100 --> 00:00:49,140
who you can contact at any time?

13
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:57,480
Or…

14
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:00,480
Do I want to hold your hand…?

15
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:05,180
I hate you for not noticing

16
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,700
But I hate myself more for not telling you anything

17
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:10,280
Because of the fear of losing you, Yeo Reum.

18
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,360
I really…do

19
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,660
hate myself…

20
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,440
Yeo Reum. Wake up.

21
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,640
We’re here.

22
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:40,920
What? Oh.

23
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,100
Wook…

24
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,560
Thanks, Wook.

25
00:01:57,320 --> 00:02:00,980
Friend; a mask to hide real feelings

26
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:15,840
A Day Before Us

